lead_paragraph: It had been so long since the Dallas Stars won a game in overtime that coach Lindy Ruff conducted a brief lesson on the bench after the third period on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Benn Wrists in Goal in OT, Stars Beat Wild 3-2
